ination within the targeted scenario makes the complex networks much more\nresistant to epidemic spreading as compared with regular lattice structures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Dec 2021 17:23:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-21"}
