 a solution to\nthe Hubble tension, as a macroscopic effect of scale dependence of the quantum\nfluctuations of the metric tensor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Dec 2021 18:41:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2022 16:18:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-09"}
