on must therefore be included in\nLSST large-scale structure analyses even though it does not significantly\nenhance the precision of the cosmological constraints.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Dec 2021 19:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2022 09:18:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-29"}
