hod,\ncarefully \"compressing'\" depth-first search traversals. Result $(iii)$ is via a\nsimpler proof of Agarwal et al. [SIAM J. Discrete Math 2019] at the expense of\npolylog factors in the expansion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Dec 2021 23:58:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-06"}
