argue for a common origin that makes these objects the youngest\nasteroid pair known to date. Questions remain regarding whether these objects\nderived from a parent comet or asteroid, and how activity may have evolved\nsince their separation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Dec 2021 02:32:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 22:38:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-04"}
