 region. In\nparticular, the inhibition of inverse energy transfer in the spanwise direction\nleads to suppression of the near-wall positive turbulent transport at large\nscales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Dec 2021 15:35:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-13"}
